The Municipal Accountant should submit the required documents; 
The Municipal Accountant and Treasurer verify whether all necessary supporting documents are attached to the disbursement vouchers before the processing of claims; 
All disbursements not attached with the required supporting documents should not be process and should be returned to their respective employee/personnel;
